    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
御別後同二日夕方、すさき港ニ着船仕候。此地の一件ハ<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">石清</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（中岡慎太郎）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>ニ申送候。<lb />
御聞取可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>下」小弟是より長崎へ廻り不日ニ上京仕候。<lb />
<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">御待可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>遣</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（おまちつかはさるべく）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>候。」別紙<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">宜</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（よろしく）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>御頼申上候。謹言。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">八月五日</seg>
<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">楳拝</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">謙吉様</seg>
右件直次郎ニ御伝奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>頼候。以上。<lb />
<lb />
